The paper deals with scheduling requests for information transmission in a wireless network, which is a problem in networked systems (cs.NI) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The focus is on minimizing power consumption, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT) and control systems (cs.SY). The paper also proposes an algorithm for the problem, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG).
